---
// Pricing.astro
---
<section id="planos" class="py-24 bg-brand-light relative z-20">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center bg-brand-yellow/10 border border-brand-yellow/30 text-brand-yellow px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold tracking-wide uppercase mb-4 shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(255,184,0,0.15)]">
        Oferta de Aniversário
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-brand-dark mb-4 tracking-tight">Escolha seu plano Ratoeira Ads</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-brand-text/80 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Garanta a melhor condição da nossa história e tenha o controle total das suas campanhas.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      
      <!-- Plano Especial -->
      <div class="relative bg-brand-card rounded-2xl p-8 border border-black/5 hover:border-brand-yellow/60 transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col group hover:shadow-[0_10px_40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)]">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-dark mb-2">Plano Anual Especial</h3>
        <p class="text-brand-text/60 mb-6 text-sm">O essencial para afiliados que querem blindar suas vendas.</p>
        
        <div class="mb-6">
          <span class="text-xs text-brand-text/40 line-through uppercase tracking-wider block mb-1">De R$ [PREÇO_ANTIGO]</span>
          <div class="flex items-end gap-2 text-brand-dark">
            <span class="text-lg font-bold">12x</span>
            <span class="text-5xl font-extrabold text-brand-yellow drop-shadow-[0_0_1px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)]">R$ [VALOR_1]</span>
          </div>
          <span class="text-brand-text/60 text-sm mt-1 block">ou R$ [VISTA_1] à vista</span>
        </div>

        <ul class="space-y-4 mb-8 flex-grow">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-brand-text/90 text-sm">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-yellow mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg>
            Bloqueio de Ips falsos e concorrentes
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-brand-text/90 text-sm">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-yellow mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg>
            Integração nativa Google Ads
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-brand-text/90 text-sm">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-yellow mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg>
            Até 10 domínios / 30.000 cliques
          </li>
        </ul>

        <a href="#checkout-link-1" class="w-full text-center bg-transparent border border-gray-200 hover:bg-brand-yellow hover:border-brand-yellow hover:text-brand-dark text-brand-dark font-bold py-3 px-4 rounded-lg transition-colors duration-300 group-hover:ring-brand-yellow/50">
          ASSINAR AGORA
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Plano Plus (Highlight) -->
      <div class="relative bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-brand-yellow flex flex-col transform md:-translate-y-4 shadow-[0_20px_50px_rgba(255,184,0,0.1)] z-10">
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 bg-brand-yellow text-brand-dark px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-extrabold tracking-widest shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(255,184,0,0.2)]">
          MAIS ESCOLHIDO
        </div>
        
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-dark mb-2">Plano Plus Anual</h3>
        <p class="text-brand-text/60 mb-6 text-sm">Completo. Para quem quer a estrutura blindada no nível máximo.</p>
        
        <div class="mb-6">
          <span class="text-xs text-brand-text/40 line-through uppercase tracking-wider block mb-1">De R$ [PREÇO_ANTIGO]</span>
          <div class="flex items-end gap-2 text-brand-dark">
            <span class="text-lg font-bold">12x</span>
            <span class="text-5xl font-extrabold text-brand-yellow drop-shadow-[0_0_2px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)]">R$ [VALOR_2]</span>
          </div>
          <span class="text-brand-text/60 text-sm mt-1 block">ou R$ [VISTA_2] à vista</span>
        </div>

        <ul class="space-y-4 mb-8 flex-grow">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-brand-dark text-sm font-medium">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-yellow mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg>
            Tudo do plano Especial
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-brand-dark text-sm font-medium">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-yellow mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg>
            Até 25 domínios / Ilimitado cliques
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-brand-yellow font-bold text-sm">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-yellow mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg>
            Suporte VIP WhatsApp
          </li>
        </ul>

        <a href="#checkout-link-2" class="w-full text-center bg-brand-yellow hover:bg-brand-yellow-hover text-brand-dark font-extrabold py-4 px-4 rounded-lg transition-transform duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 shadow-[0_5px_20px_rgba(255,184,0,0.3)]">
          GARANTIR PLANO PLUS
        </a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
